  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your imagination and IQ to crack puzzles and complete all intricate levels to save your life. Can you make it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras/e2856c6df01fc6d475b98fd4faeb8e24.avif?t=1751521633\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras_big/e2856c6df01fc6d475b98fd4faeb8e24.avif?t=1751521633 width=800 height=212 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark into an escape room-style adventure full of riddles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras/c3976d0af16bd04dbbb3c14d8e1df5c2.avif?t=1751521633\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras_big/c3976d0af16bd04dbbb3c14d8e1df5c2.avif?t=1751521633 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore weird machines that will impress you with their unique art style</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras/6c70c71496c6a501787fb179a7d180d1.avif?t=1751521633\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras_big/6c70c71496c6a501787fb179a7d180d1.avif?t=1751521633 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy tons of original puzzles, interact with buttons, levers, and little wheels to complete each level</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras/ef432ef970a869d838c38db8ccda00dc.avif?t=1751521633\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras_big/ef432ef970a869d838c38db8ccda00dc.avif?t=1751521633 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the game with your headphones to get immersed in the game at best</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras/a1892cb33705657bed26118c0d253b95.avif?t=1751521633\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras_big/a1892cb33705657bed26118c0d253b95.avif?t=1751521633 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In case you get stuck on a level, click the bulb button to get a hint that will help you solve the riddles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras/0aab9dcb244936e90ba8d446de860fc1.avif?t=1751521633\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2981690/extras_big/0aab9dcb244936e90ba8d446de860fc1.avif?t=1751521633 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will unlock a new story paragraph for each level you will complete. Discover how your kidnappers have threatened you and how it ends!</p>",
